# DrBrain — Claude Code Entry

This file is the Claude Code project entrypoint for DrBrain. It intentionally stays light:

- durable project facts and navigation live here
- reusable procedures belong in skills (AgentSkills.io standard, auto-discovered from `skills/`)
- deep reference lives in `drbrain --help`

## Quick Reference

- CLI: `drbrain --help`
- Skills: `skills/` — 16 skills covering ingest, build, embed, closure, query, reason, analysis, cartography, maintenance
- Data: `data/spool/inbox/`, `data/papers/`, `workspace/`
- Tests: `uv run pytest -m "not integration"`
- Lint: `uv run ruff check . && uv run ruff format .`
